<p t="45796" d="3237" wp="2" ws="1" p="2">​July 19XX</p>
<p t="51902" d="2903" wp="3" ws="1"><s p="3">​</s><s>​</s><s p="4">​ ​I pray that I make many friends​ ​</s><s p="3">​</s></p>
<p t="54805" d="4805" wp="3" ws="1"><s p="3">​</s><s>​</s><s p="4">​ ​and enjoy my student life to the fullest.​ ​</s><s p="3">​</s></p>
<p t="60778" d="4771" wp="3" ws="1"><s p="3">​</s><s>​</s><s p="5">​ ​If only making friends were that easy.​ ​</s><s p="3">​</s></p>
<p t="65983" d="2169" wp="3" ws="1"><s p="3">​</s><s>​</s><s p="5">​ ​I know I have to start​ ​</s><s p="3">​</s></p>
<p t="68152" d="1801" wp="3" ws="1"><s p="3">​</s><s>​</s><s p="5">​ ​by changing myself,​ ​</s><s p="3">​</s></p>
<p t="70320" d="3337" wp="3" ws="1"><s p="3">​</s><s>​</s><s p="5">​ ​but there&#39;s nothing special​ ​</s><s p="3">​
​</s><s p="5">​ ​about me to begin with.​ ​</s><s p="3">​</s></p>
<p t="73657" d="1835" wp="3" ws="1"><s p="3">​</s><s>​</s><s p="5">​ ​I can pray all I want,​ ​</s><s p="3">​</s></p>
<p t="75492" d="2836" wp="3" ws="1"><s p="3">​</s><s>​</s><s p="5">​ ​but that won&#39;t make me any friends.​ ​</s><s p="3">​</s></p>
<p t="80397" d="1669" wp="3" ws="1"><s p="3">​</s><s>​</s><s p="5">​ ​*sigh*...​ ​</s><s p="3">​</s></p>
<p t="86170" d="3770" wp="3" ws="1"><s p="3">​</s><s>​</s><s p="4">​ ​Sh-She&#39;s so beautiful...​ ​</s><s p="3">​</s></p>
<p t="89940" d="5405" wp="3" ws="1"><s p="3">​</s><s>​</s><s p="4">​ ​If only I were more like her.​ ​</s><s p="3">​
​</s><s p="4">​ ​Then I&#39;d have self-confidence.​ ​</s><s p="3">​</s></p>
<p t="96780" d="1902" wp="3" ws="1"><s p="3">​</s><s>​</s><s p="6">​ ​But, wait...​ ​</s><s p="3">​</s></p>
<p t="98682" d="2903" wp="3" ws="1"><s p="3">​</s><s>​</s><s p="6">​ ​I don&#39;t remember a girl​ ​</s><s p="3">​
​</s><s p="6">​ ​like her at Aogami High.​ ​</s><s p="3">​</s></p>
<p t="103353" d="2336" wp="2" ws="1" p="2">​The Next Day</p>
<p t="107357" d="1669" wp="3" ws="1"><s p="3">​</s><s>​</s><s p="4">​ ​So the girl I saw​ ​</s><s p="3">​</s></p>
<p t="109026" d="3136" wp="3" ws="1"><s p="3">​</s><s>​</s><s p="4">​ ​was our class&#39;s new transfer student.​ ​</s><s p="3">​</s></p>
<p t="112162" d="2937" wp="3" ws="1"><s p="3">​</s><s>​</s><s p="4">​ ​That explains why​ ​</s><s p="3">​
​</s><s p="4">​ ​I didn&#39;t recognize her.​ ​</s><s p="3">​</s></p>
<p t="116366" d="3571" wp="3" ws="1"><s p="3">​</s><s>​</s><s p="4">​ ​Her first day,​ ​</s><s p="3">​
​</s><s p="4">​ ​and she&#39;s already so popular...​ ​</s><s p="3">​</s></p>
<p t="119937" d="3670" wp="3" ws="1"><s p="3">​</s><s>​</s><s p="4">​ ​Not like it makes​ ​</s><s p="3">​
​</s><s p="4">​ ​any difference in my life.​ ​</s><s p="3">​</s></p>
<p t="126610" d="2202" wp="3" ws="1"><s p="3">​</s><s>​</s><s p="7">​ ​I know I have to start​ ​</s><s p="3">​</s></p>
<p t="128812" d="1568" wp="3" ws="1"><s p="3">​</s><s>​</s><s p="7">​ ​by changing myself...​ ​</s><s p="3">​</s></p>
<p t="135052" d="3570" wp="3" ws="1"><s p="3">​</s><s>​</s><s p="5">​ ​U-Um...​ ​</s><s p="3">​</s></p>
<p t="139790" d="2069" wp="3" ws="1"><s p="3">​</s><s>​</s><s p="5">​ ​Excuse me!​ ​</s><s p="3">​</s></p>
<p t="142226" d="1968" wp="3" ws="1"><s p="3">​</s><s>​</s><s p="5">​ ​Um,​ ​</s><s p="3">​</s></p>
<p t="144194" d="4171" wp="3" ws="1"><s p="3">​</s><s>​</s><s p="5">​ ​if it&#39;s all right with you,​ ​</s><s p="3">​
​</s><s p="5">​ ​can we be friends?​ ​</s><s p="3">​</s></p>
<p t="151068" d="2169" wp="3" ws="1"><s p="3">​</s><s>​</s><s p="8">​ ​Yes, of course!​ ​</s><s p="3">​</s></p>
<p t="153470" d="3270" wp="3" ws="1"><s p="3">​</s><s>​</s><s p="8">​ ​The pleasure&#39;s all mine!​ ​</s><s p="3">​</s></p>
<p t="157708" d="1868" wp="3" ws="1"><s p="3">​</s><s>​</s><s p="7">​ ​That was the turning point.​ ​</s><s p="3">​</s></p>
<p t="159576" d="4071" wp="3" ws="1"><s p="3">​</s><s>​</s><s p="7">​ ​I gradually began to make more friends.​ ​</s><s p="3">​</s></p>
<p t="163647" d="5572" wp="3" ws="1"><s p="3">​</s><s>​</s><s p="7">​ ​But there were some​ ​</s><s p="3">​
​</s><s p="7">​ ​who didn&#39;t look kindly​ ​</s><s p="3">​</s></p>
<p t="169219" d="2836" wp="3" ws="1"><s p="3">​</s><s>​</s><s p="7">​ ​on my friendship​ ​</s><s p="3">​
​</s><s p="7">​ ​with the popular transfer student...​ ​</s><s p="3">​</s></p>
<p t="174191" d="1301" wp="2" ws="1" p="2">​Several Days Later</p>
<p t="174191" d="3637" wp="3" ws="1"><s p="3">​</s><s>​</s><s p="9">​ ​Hey, isn&#39;t that so scary?​ ​</s><s p="3">​</s></p>
<p t="177828" d="4404" wp="3" ws="1"><s p="3">​</s><s>​</s><s p="10">​ ​That rumor about the Art Prep Room?​ ​</s><s p="3">​
​</s><s p="10">​ ​It&#39;s quite fascinating.​ ​</s><s p="3">​</s></p>
<p t="182766" d="4471" wp="3" ws="1"><s p="3">​</s><s>​</s><s p="10">​ ​Yae-san, you must have​ ​</s><s p="3">​
​</s><s p="10">​ ​heard about it from Honoka-san.​ ​</s><s p="3">​</s></p>
<p t="187237" d="2469" wp="3" ws="1"><s p="3">​</s><s>​</s><s p="9">​ ​You know about it too, Sakura-san?​ ​</s><s p="3">​</s></p>
<p t="189706" d="3137" wp="3" ws="1"><s p="3">​</s><s>​</s><s p="10">​ ​Of course. I was the one​ ​</s><s p="3">​
​</s><s p="10">​ ​who told Honoka-san about it—​ ​</s><s p="3">​</s></p>
<p t="192843" d="3437" wp="3" ws="1"><s p="3">​</s><s>​</s><s p="10">​ ​and to keep it secret.​ ​</s><s p="3">​</s></p>
<p t="197281" d="2602" wp="3" ws="1"><s p="3">​</s><s>​</s><s p="11">​ ​We Furukawas​ ​</s><s p="3">​
​</s><s p="11">​ ​built this school ourselves.​ ​</s><s p="3">​</s></p>
<p t="199883" d="2169" wp="3" ws="1"><s p="3">​</s><s>​</s><s p="11">​ ​There&#39;s no way it&#39;s haunted.​ ​</s><s p="3">​</s></p>
<p t="202052" d="3337" wp="3" ws="1"><s p="3">​</s><s>​</s><s p="12">​ ​Sure, whatever you say.​ ​</s><s p="3">​
​</s><s p="12">​ ​I&#39;m just looking forward to​ ​</s><s p="3">​</s></p>
<p t="205389" d="1701" wp="3" ws="1"><s p="3">​</s><s>​</s><s p="12">​ ​the test of courage tomorrow.​ ​</s><s p="3">​</s></p>
<p t="207090" d="2002" wp="3" ws="1"><s p="3">​</s><s>​</s><s p="13">​ ​And the more the merrier!​ ​</s><s p="3">​</s></p>
<p t="209092" d="2703" wp="3" ws="1"><s p="3">​</s><s>​</s><s p="13">​ ​We should invite Shino-san​ ​</s><s p="3">​
​</s><s p="13">​ ​and the new girl!​ ​</s><s p="3">​</s></p>
<p t="212696" d="4404" wp="3" ws="1"><s p="3">​</s><s>​</s><s p="11">​ ​Misora-san&#39;s stuck to her​ ​</s><s p="3">​
​</s><s p="11">​ ​like glue again, I see.​ ​</s><s p="3">​</s></p>
<p t="217100" d="1368" wp="3" ws="1"><s p="3">​</s><s>​</s><s p="11">​ ​Such a nuisance.​ ​</s><s p="3">​</s></p>
<p t="218468" d="1569" wp="3" ws="1"><s p="3">​</s><s>​</s><s p="12">​ ​Aww, cut her some slack.​ ​</s><s p="3">​</s></p>
<p t="220037" d="3670" wp="3" ws="1"><s p="3">​</s><s>​</s><s p="12">​ ​You&#39;re just jealous &#39;cause​ ​</s><s p="3">​
​</s><s p="12">​ ​you&#39;re into the new girl yourself.​ ​</s><s p="3">​</s></p>
<p t="223707" d="1702" wp="3" ws="1"><s p="3">​</s><s>​</s><s p="11">​ ​I didn&#39;t ask your opinion.​ ​</s><s p="3">​</s></p>
<p t="225409" d="4738" wp="3" ws="1"><s p="3">​</s><s>​</s><s p="11">​ ​My head hurts just​ ​</s><s p="3">​
​</s><s p="11">​ ​looking at Misora-san...​ ​</s><s p="3">​</s></p>
<p t="232983" d="2469" wp="3" ws="1"><s p="3">​</s><s>​</s><s p="10">​ ​...​ ​</s><s p="3">​</s></p>
<p t="235452" d="2669" wp="2" ws="1" p="14">​9 PM, The Next Day</p>
<p t="239489" d="2103" wp="3" ws="1"><s p="3">​</s><s>​</s><s p="5">​ ​This is so exciting...​ ​</s><s p="3">​</s></p>
<p t="243994" d="3103" wp="3" ws="1"><s p="3">​</s><s>​</s><s p="9">​ ​Oh! This way, this way!​ ​</s><s p="3">​</s></p>
<p t="247998" d="1134" wp="3" ws="1"><s p="3">​</s><s>​</s><s p="10">​ ​Well...​ ​</s><s p="3">​</s></p>
<p t="249132" d="2837" wp="3" ws="1"><s p="3">​</s><s>​</s><s p="10">​ ​it looks like we&#39;re all here.​ ​</s><s p="3">​
​</s><s p="10">​ ​Let&#39;s begin.​ ​</s><s p="3">​</s></p>
<p t="4989" d="100" wp="4" ws="2" p="15">​</p>
